latestIgtvVideos.title: Dahi Bhalla.
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
Dahi Bhalla is prepared by soaking vadas in thick Dahi. 

It is a sumptuous dish, made with curd and some easy spices and veggies that can be easy available.
I have come up with simple recipe of preparing this delicious Dahi Bhalla.

latestIgtvVideos.title: Chhupari:View from Thamti Temple
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
https://youtu.be/ooa_ZwCBVr8

CHHUPARI: Village chhupari is the last village situated just below the hills of #Bollon. There is this small temple on top of this village called "Thamti Temple". From here you can view the beautiful sites of #Jubbal and #Rohru area. Bhaloon hill is popular for the OM which is said to be a natural creation of god which can be clearly seen from #Thamti temple. In the heart of the village, there is a beautiful wood architecture temple of local DEVTA #GUDARU JI & #LANKRA VEER.
The village is well connected by road which 19 Km from Rohru.
So if in case you visit  Rohru don't forget to pay your visit to my village and explore one of best views of Jubbal and Rohru valley ... Our village peoples always Welcomes you🙏🏻
